one who recites YAA NAAFE’O frequently on the Eve of Friday (shab’e Juma) will achieve closeness to Allah (swt), and if he goes in between the enemies will remain safe and steady.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Ma’soom (a) se marwi hai keh jo shakhs YAA NAAFE’O ka vird shab’e Juma mein ziyadah se ziyadah kiya kare to qurb’e Ilaahi (Khuda se nazdiki) haasil kar lega, agar be-shumaar dushmano ke darmiyaan bhi chala jaayega to sahih o salaamat rahega.", "UrduDescription": "معصومؑ سے مروی ہے کہ جو شخص ’’یَا نَافِعُ‘‘ کا شب جمعہ میں زیادہ سے زیادہ ورد کیا کرے تو قرب الٰہی حاصل کرلے گا اگر بے شمار دشمنوں کے درمیان بھی چلا جائے گا تو صحیح و سلامت رہے گا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicR