Sign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010359, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 5, "EnglishDescription": "If a person starts reciting YAA NAAFE’O from Thursday and on every Eve of Friday (shab’e Juma) recites 603 times for 6 Friday will be independent in obvious and hidden, all his enemy will be conquered, will get profit in all his work from the start. Beside this he will be beneficial among people, he will have purity and will always overpower.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Jo shakhs Thursday ke din YAA NAAFE’O ka vird shuru kare aur 6 shab’e Juma mein har dafa 603 martaba YAA NAAFE’O ka vird kare to woh shakhs zaahir o baatin mein mustaghni (be-neyaaz) hoga, us ke tamaam dushman maghloob (pastt) honge, har kaam aur eqdaam (shuruwaat) mein nafa haasil karega. Is ke alaawah us ka nafa tamaam logo’n ko pohonchega, us mein paakeezgi hogi aur hamesha ghaalib rahega waghera waghera.", "UrduDescription": "جو شخص جمعرات کے دن ’’یَا نَافِعُ‘‘ کا ورد شروع کرے اور چھ شب جمعہ میں ہر دفعہ 603 مرتبہ ’’یَا نَافِعُ‘‘ کا ورد کرے تو وہ شخص ظاہر و باطن میں مستغنی ہوگا، اس کے تمام دشمن مغلوب ہوں گے، ہر کام اور اقدام میں نفع حاصل کرے گا، اس کے علاوہ اس کا نفع تمام لوگوں کو پہنچے گا، اس میں پاکیزگی ہوگی اور ہمیشہ غالب رہے گا وغیرہ وغیرہ۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12"